      "id": "INTJ",
      "name": {
        "zh": "建筑师",
        "en": "Architect"
      },
      "subtitle": {
        "zh": "富有想象力和战略性的思想家",
        "en": "Imaginative and strategic thinkers"
      },
      "description": {
        "zh": "INTJ 是十六种 MBTI 人格类型中最罕见的类型之一，约占人口的 2%。他们以其深刻的分析能力、独立的思维和追求完美的特质而闻名。INTJ 通常被称为「建筑师」，因为他们擅长设计和构建宏伟的计划。",
        "en": "INTJ is one of the rarest of the 16 MBTI types, comprising about 2% of the population. They are known for their deep analytical abilities, independent thinking, and pursuit of perfection. INTJs are often called 'Architects' because of their talent for designing and constructing grand plans."
      },
